{"tid":184484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你係香港人 粵人 台灣人  中國人 華人 華裔？","createTime":"2017-04-02T23:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T13:24:25.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85e20cf2ef9e0096a8ccff981329827c282f8e91","tid":184484,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T23:44:27.000Z","msg":"華人=北方華夏民族<br />\n(china古代最初支那指長江北中原地域) <br />\n閩粵人=南方百越民族<br />\n粵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人係粵裔 港裔 =\\ 華人 華裔 <br />\n台灣人係台裔=\\ 華人 華裔"},{"pid":"655be64ca81ac86ad65f8a19e43609945afef077","tid":184484,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"粵人係南蠻，一定唔係漢族<br />\n如果華人係講種族就一定唔會同北佬一樣<br />\n唔洗討論咩中國人嘅血<br />\n中華民國成立時，嗰陣香港係英國地方，講國籍就更加唔會係中國人/華人<br />\n所以睇你點界定華人<br />\n係種族上，香港多數都係南蠻，南蠻就傳統上都唔係漢人，亦冇理由會係華人，當然你可以屈成吉思汗同慈禧係華人，噉就冇嘢好討論啦"},{"pid":"f2d3b422bb08be1bdfaac2cc5c3fb53ed83e1395","tid":184484,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"港裔英國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4574b690f53a79228ebd6e3772be011a1f5e74dc","tid":184484,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T12:49:19.000Z","msg":"漢裔"},{"pid":"09f940d46679be010a10b392515c25e80a35f1d4","tid":184484,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T12:57:48.000Z","msg":"南越人"},{"pid":"59bf66cd8197a213c3ca5f59f7f09dccb4e6f799","tid":184484,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"南粵港人"}]}